  <!-- EN: advanced ammunition -->
  <CE_AdvancedAmmo.label>先进弹药</CE_AdvancedAmmo.label>
  <!-- EN: Allows for the production of advanced ammunition for small arms and light weapons systems like armor-piercing incendiary, sabot, and high-explosive rounds. -->
  <CE_AdvancedAmmo.description>允许生产小型武器和轻武器系统的先进弹药，如穿甲燃烧弹、高爆弹。</CE_AdvancedAmmo.description>
  <!-- EN:
    <li>subject->advanced ammunition</li>
    <li>subject->ammunition fillings</li>
    <li>subject_story->stumbled across a cache of advanced weapons</li>
    <li>subject_story->learned to use a discarding sabot to defeat powered armor</li>
    <li>subject_story->worked for a prolific arms dealer</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->creating explosive ammunition</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->crafting discarding sabots</li>
  -->
  <CE_AdvancedAmmo.generalRules.rulesStrings>
    <li>subject->先进弹药</li>
    <li>subject->弹药填充物</li>
    <li>subject_story->偶然发现了一批先进武器的藏匿处</li>
    <li>subject_story->学会使用脱壳穿甲弹击败动力装甲</li>
    <li>subject_story->曾为一位高产的军火商工作</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->制造爆炸性弹药</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->制作脱壳穿甲弹</li>
  </CE_AdvancedAmmo.generalRules.rulesStrings>
  
  <!-- EN: advanced launchers -->
  <CE_AdvancedLaunchers.label>复杂发射器</CE_AdvancedLaunchers.label>
  <!-- EN: Allows for the production of more advanced launchers and munitions like the incendiary, triple rocket, or doomsday launcher and time-fuzed explosives. -->
  <CE_AdvancedLaunchers.description>允许生产更先进的发射器，如燃烧弹发射器，三重火箭发射器和末日火箭发射器。</CE_AdvancedLaunchers.description>
